items.name: Bison(Arknights)
items.description:
Intro

This model is trained on the public illustrations of the Bison(Arknights).

Version 1.5 beta

In this version, I use Lion optimizer and add "bison\(arknights\)" a trigger word to summarize the face character. It is for that sometimes Ver1.0 may draw a hair-like horn so that it's like the boy has 3 horns.

Also, the trigger word "bison\(outfit\)" controls the boy's cloth, if he doesn't want to wear it, add a "white jacket" to persuade him to.

However, Version 1.5 may not seem to be as familiar as Version 1.0 can do. But it works better on mixed models, here we present some result simply using Super-Merger to mix other stylized models on the Anything Family, so that we can have Bison in more styles, not only in anime style!

Still, as Bison is still a young boy, if u use some magic prompts, he may look even younger.

Thanks for downloading and testing, enjoy yourself!

Version 1.0

It works well with non-style anime models such as Anything Family, for pastel-style models and others (i.e., SoftPastel, Yaoi and Pastel2D) you will get a detailed kemono cow-boy but not the same as Bison the character.

Baseline is that the stylized model can draw cow ears but cannot draw cow horns unless forced it to, so you could use this on other models to draw yourself a cow boy.

It's my first Lora trying so if you have any suggestions please tell me. With much appreciation.

TRY OUT ALL VERSONS

Spent several hours curating and selecting a set of 29 very old hand-painted photographs from China and Japan, which have been used as the basis for training these embeddings. This means that when you use these embeddings to generate your own images, you will be able to recreate the aesthetic and style of these ancient photographs with remarkable accuracy and detail. Try experimenting with futuristic prompts of characters. This TI embedding works great with most fine tuned checkpoints.

PS: Use the generation parameters of the sample images provided and then try experimenting with different combinations. Do share your generations, I would love to see them. Thank You

items.description:
11th Release, 堕姫 - Daki from Kimetsu no Yaiba.

Put everything in Filter for seeing all images!

Examples Image is now active, Click on Show more for Weight & Trigger recommendation, Also click on About This Version at Right Corner for more Info.

I didn't not find a Lora on Daki & Not so much Art on it, so again i created a LORA Like MTSpider.

This Lora is trained on 114+ Images with Good quality, I sorted everything manually, Only picked the best possible. (SFW + NFSW)

AnimeFullFinalPrunedFP16 used, so he work with the majority of Anime Model, you can see in examples images. (Abyss Model + 7th Corneo's Heaven's Model.)

Well, he can do Default Skin with Black hair & Demon Skin with Multicolored Hair White & Green Hair.

About Trigger Words & Prompts: DakiV4 (For Trigger) & for prompts just refer to examples image.

Weight recommended: 0.6-1. - Sometime weight at 1 is too strong so the Best result is 0.8.

Negative Embedding used: EasyNegative, BadPrompt2.

Leave a Review & Share you're image in comments if you appreciate this Work :).

items.name: Z_phyr Noise Transformation
items.description:
(Example for simplification only). Imagine a histogram of any generated image. What does noise offset do? It completely shifts this histogram to the left or right, as if you were changing the exposure on the camera. Instead, I suggest stretching/normalizing both ends of the histogram so that they occupy the entire color space and at the same time there are no too sharp transitions along its entire length. (I tried to depict the function on the last graph, it looks like the “Curves” tool in Photoshop). This affects only those U-Net blocks that are responsible for color, brightness and detail, while almost not affecting the blocks of the general composition of the frame. The strength of application can be controlled in the same way as when merging noise offset.

（仅为简化而设的示例）。想象一下任何生成图像的直方图。噪声偏移会做什么？它完全将这个直方图向左或向右移动，就像你在相机上改变曝光一样。相反，我建议拉伸/归一化直方图的两端，使它们占据整个色彩空间，同时在其整个长度上没有太大的跳变。（我试图在最后一个图上描绘这个函数，它看起来像Photoshop中的“曲线”工具）。这只影响那些负责颜色、亮度和细节的U-Net块，而几乎不影响帧的总体构图块。应用的强度可以像合并噪声偏移一样进行控制。

(Пример исключительно для упрощения понимания). Представим гистограмму любого сгенерированного изображения. Что делает смещение шума? Полностью смещает эту гистограмму влево или вправо, как если бы вы меняли экспозицию на фотоаппарате. Вместо этого я предлагаю растянуть/нормализовать оба конца гистограммы так, чтобы они занимали всё цветовое пространство и при этом не было бы слишком резких перепадов на всём его протяжении. (Попытался изобразить функцию на последнем графике, она похожа на инструмент "Кривые" в Фотошопе). При этом затрагиваются только те блоки U-Net, которые отвечают за цветность, светлость и детализацию, при этом почти не затрагивая блоки общей композиции кадра. Силу применения можно контролировать точно так же, как при подмешивании смещения шума.

items.name: Mistoon_Amethyst
items.description:
You can now get all my LoRAs in one single package if you subscribe to my Patreon (including those not on CivitAI):

The Complete Catalog Download | Patreon

How to use this

If you are new to the world of Stable Diffusion, you can learn how to run it by yourself here:

Tutorial

You'll also need a VAE to use this. For the examples, I've used the Grapefruit one:

https://huggingface.co/iZELX1/Grapefruit/resolve/main/Grapefruit.vae.pt

What's new in v2?

I wasn't satisfied by the overall performance of the checkpoint. It often used the same colors and required a low CFG level. With the newer model, you can use a higher CFG level without over saturation and distortion. It's less Disney-ish and more a crossover of vintage western and modern anime style (which is what I wanted to create in the first place).

What's this model

Mistoon_Amethyst is a variant of my SD model Mistoon_Sapphire that tries to achieve a Disney pinup style.

The starting point for this model was my blend. From there, I then added a few of my custom LoRAs in the mix to change the esthetic (mostly Pear and Contact).

Try also the other flavors:

The style

It creates realistic and expressive characters with a "disney" twist.

All the examples have been created using this version of the model using my workflow. Check the guide if you want to learn more about my workflow.

The model can also easily do NSFW stuff (check the last examples).

Right now the model is biased over sea backgrounds and cyan clothes (for whatever reason), so I highly recommend addind those to the negative prompt.

Guides

Learn how to create pictures like mine with my step-by-step tutorials:

LoRA and Picture Commissions

items.name: SDArt : Futuristic Fashion
items.description:
Model presentation

This is a model related to the "Challenge of the WeekEnd" contest on Stable Diffusion discord.

You can find this dataset in a more complete model, SDArt : Complete Edition.

This present version is trained on dedicated tokens per user, and doesn't work like you may be used to.

I try to make a model out of all the submissions, for people to continue enjoy the theme after the event, and see a little of their designs in other people's creations. The token stays "SDArt" and I balance the learning on the low side, so that it doesn't just replicate creations.

The pictures were tagged using the token "SDArt", and an arbitrary token given to the user that submitted it.

The dataset is available below and is composed of 31 pictures.


This week's theme

[LOG #77 X-7829F TRANSCRIPT]

Hello..? Is this recording?

This may be sudden and surprising but.. I'm from the future! Well, a future.

I found a watch that allowed me to project into the past - I was a little skeptical at first but figured it was worth a shot. So, I dialed in 2023 and appeared in front of a group of people in some sort of white coats who were wearing some seriously outdated clothing. I chuckled to myself and told them about our tech-infused fashion in my future. They started experimenting with new materials and designs, and before I knew it, they were creating some impressive pieces!

Of course, I couldn't resist sending a few more messages back in time. I gave them some hints for creating even more innovative fashion, and they ate it up. It was amazing to see how my small advice could change the course of history.

As I projected closer and closer into the future, I could see the world evolving around items of clothing. One of the designers caught my eye with their creation of a smart jacket. The jacket was made with a special fabric that could regulate body temperature and adjust itself according to the weather. Another designer had created a dress that could change color based on your mood. How cool is that? Talk about wearing your emotions on your sleeve!

But the pièce de résistance was a pair of shoes that could charge your phone! Yes, you heard that right. The shoes had a built-in charger that converted the kinetic energy generated by walking into electrical energy. Gone were the days of simple aesthetics. Fashion had evolved into something that was not only innovative but also functional.

And so, here we are in 20XX! Who knows, maybe we'll have fashion that can teleport us to different dimensions next...

...

Oh.

COW #1 - FUTURISTIC FASHION

Step into the future and create a character! :mm:

Explore the world of high-tech fashion where style intersects innovation. In this future, fashion is not just an art form but a reflection of technological possibilities.

Challenges:

  • Use artificial lighting such as LEDs and neon signs to illuminate your subject.

  • Incorporate a tech gadget or device into your fashion design in a creative and functional way.

  • Use a neon color palette in your art.

I try to make a model out of all the submissions, for people to continue enjoy the theme after the event, and see a little of their designs in other people's creations. The token stays "SDArt" and I balance the learning on the low side, so that it doesn't just replicate creations.

The pictures were tagged using the token "SDArt", and an arbitrary token given to the user that submitted it.

The dataset is available below and is composed of 39 pictures.


This week's theme

In a world where colors have flavor, and sounds have texture,

The senses intertwine to create a sensory rapture.

Welcome to “Synesthesia”- where the ordinary is extraordinary,

And art takes on a meaning that’s truly visionary! :Rainbowpink:

Synesthesia /ˌsɪn.əsˈθiː.ʒə/: an anomalous blending of the senses in which the stimulation of one modality simultaneously produces sensation in a different modality. Synesthetes hear colors, feel sounds, and taste shapes.

  • Create an image that captures the essence of synesthesia sensory! Explore the intersections of sound, color, and texture. What’s it like tasting a melody, feeling a scent, or seeing colored words?

  • What would it look it look like to taste the sound of a thunderstorm? How would you visualize the sensation of feeling the warmth of the sun on your skin? Or how about tasting a particular color–such as a bright red apple or a cool blueberry?

  • Explore the possibilities of synesthesia and its many interpretations!

items.name: Setsuna Meiou ( Sailor Pluto Fanart ) - Sailor Moon
items.description:
V2:

Seems V1 was too flexible and scared noobs, noob then gave it a bad review and all it's momentum fizzled away. So I simplified the triggers in this one to try to make it a bit more fool proof.

works fine with: <lora:SetsunaMeiouV2:.7>, SetsunaMeiou, <outfit>

I only isolated 3 things:

  • Pluto_sailor_senshi_uniform: Her classic outfit. I think her stars variant uniform's only difference is her star choker. There're a couple of images but not enough to isolate it.

  • Setsuna_Purple_Teacher_Dress_Suit: Her dress when teaching at Infinity Gakuen? (Unless it's mandela effect.)

  • staff_GarnetRod: This one is iffy and totally gacha. I made an effort for it to learn the shape but it can come up split or weird angles or with a faulty grip. You might get better results on controlnet but currently it has about 1:10 odd of appearing correclty. Adding holding_staff might help somewhat.

As always the tag summary is inside the dataset so people can experiment further.

V1:

I gathered the dataset at the same time I did the Haruka and Michiru Lora. I considered doing an adult Sailor Saturn one but that is for the future as finding enough of her images as an adult can be a bit of a challenge. Regardless here we have the Sailor Pluto and the eternal doubt is garnet red or brown? Why does her outfit changes color whenever when it is supposed to be garnet and black? Are her eyes red, purple, pink or a mixture of all three?

Seems the LORA starts going bonkers at about .8 strength I think the sailor_senshi_uniform tag is overtrained in the NAI model family. Her nose seems to go bonkers(oversimplified it) some times due to some original manga images that maybe i should have pruned.

Her hair and eye color can drift a bit so to be safe use green_hair, hair_bun, red_eyes. It also like to eat her hair bun so better add it.

I got good results using: <lora:SetsunaMeiou:0.5>, SetsunaMeiou, green_hair, hair_bun, red_eyes, big_breasts, standing, black_sailor_collar, black_skirt, black_choker, solo, sailor_senshi_uniform, tiara, gloves

Some likely useful tags are:

  • sailor_senshi_uniform

  • black_sailor_collar

  • black_skirt

  • black_choker

  • high_heel_boots

  • bow

  • back_bow

  • staff

For extra experimentation with the tags, I will add the tag summary inside the training data.

items.name: Timerra from Fire Emblem
items.description:
The model was created from 21 pictures from the video game Fire Emblem Engage, mostly in-game cinematics and artist's pictures. And was trained on AbyssOrangeMiX3 model from WarriorMama777

I used the Lora Training Colab from Hollowstrawberry and my own Dataset to train the model.

Here is a recommended sample prompt for Timerra (you may try other outfit, like dress, swimsuit ....) :

1girl, bike shorts, multicolored white pink crop top, navel, multicolored frilled_skirt, dark-skinned_female, jewelry, long_hair, ponytail, hair ornament flower hairband, multicolored beads bubbles, brown_eyes, symbol-shaped pupils star \(symbol\), (red_eyes:0.66), black_eyes ; <lora:timerra-v3-10:0.75>

Kaidras created a Lora for this character; I haven't  tested it. I began to create the dataset two weeks ago, before he released it. This Lora is independent of his LoRa.

If you have any advice, please tell me.

items.name: 村里发的魅魔VillageSuccubus
items.description:
快回来，村里发魅魔了~

Come back soon, the village has assigned succubus (a kind of Chinese Internet meme)

开发记录：暂时不会开发v5版本，有些别的东西想先弄，后续v5的话，估计改用dim128重新训练试试多种形态的兼容性会不会更好，训练素材也会更精简一点

Development record: The v5 version will not be developed for the time being. I want to get some other things first. If I continue to develop v5 in the future, it is estimated to use dim128 for retraining. Will it be better to try the compatibility of various triggers?

推荐权重：0.3-0.6，Hi-res时适当提高，重绘幅度建议小一点

Recommended weight: 0.3-0.6, appropriate increase in Hi-res, denoising is recommended to be smaller

prompt问题：

1、realistic类咒语会明显削弱翅膀和尾巴，小幅削弱淫纹，可自行补充wings、horns、tattoo等

2、demon词缀包括demon_wings这样的都会改变妆容，建议不要加，如果喜欢的话自己看

3、一个lora里多种发色分别绑定还是很难搞，我最后单独训练了一轮electricmage想绑定金发最后还是很不稳定，建议还是自己加yellow_hair之类的，当然好处是也可以换你自己想要的发色

prompt question:

1. Realistic prompts will significantly weaken wings and tails, and slightly weaken tattoos. You can supplement wings, horns, tattoos, etc.

2. Demon affixes including demon_wings will change the makeup. It is recommended not to add it. If you like it, try it yourself

3. It is still very difficult to bind multiple hair colors in one lora separately. I finally trained a round of electricmage alone to bind blonde hair, but it was still very unstable. It is recommended to add yellow_hair by yourself. Of course, the advantage is that you can also change the hair color you want

水印问题：恶魔外形感觉和同人网站水印有强关联，出现概率贼高，但是去水印负面加的太高会影响图片质量甚至削到淫纹头上，建议还是允许出现水印然后修图或裁切

Watermark problem: The appearance of the devil is strongly related to some website watermarks, and the probability of occurrence is very high

However, if the negative watermark is added too high, it will affect the quality of the picture and even scratch the tattoo. It is recommended to allow the watermark to appear and then edit or crop the picture.

关键词及世界观设定解读（絮絮叨叨）

1girl：隐藏形态，但角经常会幻化为兽耳或发髻，而且腰比普通瘦的女性会细20%，疑似肋骨和内脏比人类更少或更小

Village_Succubus：恶魔特征的角、翼、尾，眼睛有时会变色，四肢有时自带长筒手套、长筒袜的纹路，或者鳞片、咒文类的纹路

obscenity_tattoo：魅魔魔力的显现，特点为爱心形状的淫纹，魅魔魔力越强，爱心越多越大越精致，有的魅魔不喜欢显露淫纹，有的魅魔反之只显露淫纹不张开翅膀

darkness_tattoo：遇到抖M忍不住黑化的魅魔形态，黑皮白毛+夜光纹身，战斗力和“战斗力”都更强

扩展关键词-魔力专精

icemage：专精冰魔法的魅魔，常见发色为浅蓝偏白色，喜欢的就职方向是圣女、医生

firemage：专精火魔法的魅魔，常见发色为红色、橘色，喜欢的就职方向是厨师、焰火师

windmage：专精风魔法的魅魔，常见发色为绿色、青色，喜欢的就职方向是忍者、旅行家

electricmage：专精电魔法的魅魔，常见发色为金色，喜欢的就职方向是机甲少女（赛博格？）、陷阱师

备注

（搞不定翅膀和尾巴，明明训练都是双翼、负面也试着排除single_wing，就是乱七八糟，偶尔自动变成head_wings但还算能看，侧身和背后的位置识别也是离谱，估摸着要专门训练或者我有空去学习一下controlnet试试……

最难的尾巴正面我都没让他稳定下来，偶尔还会和淫纹混淆，只能暂时放弃了，我还是很想要爱心尾巴的。

淫纹还算成功，真人模型用各种tattoo跑出来的感觉太丑了，长个鬼脸兽头看着不碍眼吗，所以也专门练了一下爱心tattoo）

items.name: 【Art Style】Jeneral Style
items.description:
Introduction

A Lycoris model trained with ~260 images by Jeneral. The trigger tag is ‘jeneral’. The 784mb VAEs (NovelAI, Anythingv3, Orangemix, Counterfeit) are recommended. 0.6 ~ 0.8 weights are good. The preview images are generated using 1.6 version (original) YesMix.

Cautions (Must Read)

  • Some preview images are generated using hires fix. Thus, if you wanna generate the preview images, pls download the original preview images and analyze them using 'PNG INFO' in webui to get all generating information.

  • The maximum of generating resolution should not exceed 1024 theoretically, otherwise extra/deformed head/limbs will be waiting for you :). Try to use 'hires fix' to prevent this problem and help to generate higher-resolution images.

  • For 784mb VAEs (NovelAI, Anythingv3, Orangemix, Counterfeit) users, make sure add '--no-half-vae' in command line of webui to prevent generating black images. See voldy's log for the details of edit method. For high-performance GPU, make sure 'medvram' and 'lowvram' mode are disabled.

items.name: Beidou [Genshin Impact]
items.description:
This is my first attempt of making a LoRA. I know that another Beidou LoRA already exists on the site, but i wasn't satisfied with it results, hence i decided to make one myself. I want to thank @Hollowstrawberry for the collab he made. And also @rockerBOO, @ChameleonAI, @zykurv, @IndolentCat for their tips and tricks! The reviews and feedback will be very valuable for me.

My goal was to make it very versatile and accessible for simple prompting (you will get better results with high prompting skills), so you can use any outfit or any hairstyle whatever your creativity and fantasy could lead to. This LoRA is capabable of making NSFW if you want to.

The main trigger word:

is beidouep. To recreate Beidou's original outfit you will need some extra triggers such as: start with ogoutfit that's was my main idea how to separate generations for variety; hair stick — her unique hairpin, i don't recommend using any other words to describe it; fingerless gloves, fur trim, thigh boots, pelvic curtain. Those are main components of her original outfit and you can use them in negative prompt as well. You can also try adding cleavage cutout if it's not showing up or you can add that to negative prompt if you don't want it.

Next to her eyepatch:

it always will be on different eyes, this is because training done with flipped images and also some of her fanart is just made with wrong eyepatch placement. If eyepatch is not showing up (this can happen on some models), I found an interesting trick during testing: you can add one eye covered to prompt and 98% of the time it will show up. On some models it works fine without it, but if you seeing that you current model struggling with it, add it to prompt.

Weights:

This LoRA was trained on AnyLora from @Lykon, so sweet spot for it is 0.7, however depending on the model you using you might want to adjust that. Especially if you will be trying to use it with realistic models. I think it works fine with semi-realistic models, I have not tried it with realistic models.

I'm not sure what name LoRA will get on downloading, so please make sure you using the proper name in prompt of the file that you downloaded if you going to copy prompts from previews.

Negative embeddings:

Two negative embeddings were used in preview prompts (pay attention to weights):
https://civitai.com/models/7808/easynegative
https://civitai.com/models/16993/badhandv4-animeillustdiffusion
